#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.21:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga "
msgstr "3. Persons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Samiddhasutta "
msgstr "21. With Saviṭṭha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.21:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an3.21:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: samiddho → saviṭṭho (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: mahākoṭṭhiko → mahākoṭṭhito (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.21:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ca samiddho āyasmā ca mahākoṭṭhiko yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Saviṭṭha and Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita went up to Venerable Sāriputta, and exchanged greetings with him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.21:1.4"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ samiddhaṃ āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they sat down to one side and Venerable Sāriputta said to Venerable Saviṭṭha, "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.21:2.1"
msgid "“Tayome, āvuso samiddha, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverend Saviṭṭha, these three people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.21:2.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

#. VAR: diṭṭhippatto → diṭṭhappatto (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an3.21:2.3"
msgid "Kāyasakkhī, diṭṭhippatto, saddhāvimutto. "
msgstr "The personal witness, the one attained to view, and the one freed by faith. "

msgctxt "an3.21:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, āvuso, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world. "

msgctxt "an3.21:2.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ, āvuso, tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ katamo te puggalo khamati abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "Of these three people, who do you believe to be the finest?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.21:3.1"
