msgctxt "an3.21:3.4"
msgid "Ime kho, āvuso, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world. "

#. VAR: yvāyaṃ → yoyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.21:3.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ, āvuso, tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ yvāyaṃ puggalo saddhāvimutto, ayaṃ me puggalo khamati imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro ca. "
msgstr "Of these three people, I believe the person freed by faith to be finest. "

msgctxt "an3.21:3.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an3.21:3.7"
msgid "Imassa, āvuso, puggalassa saddhindriyaṃ adhimattan”ti. "
msgstr "Because this person’s faculty of faith is outstanding.” "

